title.narrative: Project Support costs

description.narrative: Limited resources available for the program had a considerable impact on performance in 2021. Owing to limited available resources, the programme had to reprioritize activities to focus on the elimination of Open Defecation. Regarding the implementation of the work plan, a limited number of partnership agreements were established covering mainly emergency preparedness and response as well as KRC related activities.A considerable part of the allocation of the year was consigned to the elaboration of the ODF roadmap that is deemed key to improving the sector ability to engage donors and investment. | Status:Met | As-of Date:26/01/2022
